title: slimepaperunreleasedsketchbook
description:
Previously unreleased sketchbook from Lars Nielsen circa Christmastime 2008 and on, with a rather short amount of content and art because of another sketchbook acquired around the same time. this sketchbook was then used periodically throughout the year in short intervals, with sketches ranging from Zitboy production work to a homework list. Only one page is missing and is in current possession by the fine artist Ron Spencer and a scan of the page is currently being acquired.  Anyway, if your reading this and downloading/torrenting this, its because it was sent this to you as some sort of unconditional gift friend thing. And lars wanted to try his hand at making a torrent file.

Man, I&#039;m writing in third person, this is totally balls to the walls bitchin.

	Anyway, please don&#039;t go distributing this willy nilly. I try to keep this stuff disclosed to good buddies that i can trust. Hopefully you&#039;ll do the same. Oh, and hey! if this is well received, i&#039;ll do another full sketchbook release! A bigger, longer, and better illustrated one.  SO, without further ado, enjoy!  I hope you like this little collection of oddities!


	See ya,
			
		Lars Nielsen
